Make Me A Video Game!

I the happy and slow Ashley have sawJoe's cute sister and plan to steal her leaky They!

What are a Hippo and backpacking mouse to do? Before you can help Renee, you'll have to collect the beautiful we and shy us that open up the 44 worlds connected to A Ashley's Lair. There are 3 they and 6 we in the game, along with hundreds of other goodies for you to find.